; Coverage: commodity.cc (compare_by_commodity price comparison
; with different price commodities -- recursion finds disparity)
; Two lots of the same commodity with prices in different currencies

2024/01/01 Buy in USD
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL {$150.00}
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Buy in EUR
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {100.00 EUR}
    Assets:Cash

test bal --lot-prices Assets:Brokerage
      10 AAPL {$150}
     5 AAPL {EUR100}  Assets:Brokerage
end test
